"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=fifa+world+cup","The Road to World Cup 2026: What to expect from the biggest teams","https://www.foxsports.com/stories/soccer/road-world-cup-2026-where-top-teams-stand-one-year-go","Thu, 12 Jun 2025 01:31:00 GMT","


