"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=site:entertainmentnow.com","DWTS' Daniella Karagach Says Sasha Farber Is a ‘Third Wheel' in Her Relationship","https://entertainmentnow.com/dancing-with-the-stars/dwts-daniella-karagach-sasha-farber-relationship/","Thu, 12 Jun 2025 15:47:43 GMT","

Amid the news that “Dancing With the Stars” professional dancer Sasha Farber has split from his girlfriend, “The Bachlorette” star Jenn Tran, it appears his fellow dancers are rallying around him to show their support. Daniella Karagach has discussed how she and husband Pasha Pashkov spend a lot of time with Farber, and that he has become a part of their relationship.

A post shared by Sasha Farber (@sashafarber1)

“He's our throuple,” Karagach told Us Weekly on June 11. “He's literally our third wheel. We take him everywhere. I'm not kidding.” She also shared that they spend so much time together that they feel like family, and commented on how amazing Farber is with their daughter, Nikita (she was born in May 2023).

“We love him. We get together all the time. We're either in his house or he's in our house,” Karagach said. “Kiki loves him. Sasha's like our kid. We adopted Sasha, even though he's older than us. We've adopted Sasha now.”

A post shared by Sasha Farber (@sashafarber1)

If Farber has found himself newly single, at least he has plenty of support. But what happened between him and Tran? The pair first met when they competed together on DWTS Season 33. Their chemistry was obvious and fans immediately speculated about whether their onscreen connection had become something more.

The pair never confirmed they were a couple, but People reports that a source said they have split after almost a year of dating but remain “very good friends.”

Farber and Tran have both been active on social media since the news of their split was announced. Both have shared videos that have nothing to do with their relationship, but in the comment section of Tran's cooking video, which she posted on Instagram on June 10, some fans have expressed their sadness. “I'm so sad in what I read on TMZ,” a comment reads. “But I hope you guys remain friends and you each find someone to love we wish you both the best.” Another fan also weighed in, writing, “Miss your Sasha and Jenn content.”

“Not related to this buuut…. Are you and sash still together!?” a fan asked.

If the couple were dating, and again, fans are convinced they were, then what is the reason for their split? People reports that the split was amicable and Us Weekly reports that a source told them “they're no longer seeing each other.” The source adds that Tran is “focusing hard on her studies and not letting anything else get in the way of her goals right now,” Us Weekly reports. 

