"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=site:indiewire.com","Colin Trevorrow Knows How Heartbreaking Filmmaking Can Be — He Wants to Change That with His Own Production Company","https://www.indiewire.com/features/interviews/colin-trevorrow-production-company-star-wars-1235131479/","Thu, 12 Jun 2025 13:30:00 GMT","

