"https://news.google.com/rss/search?q=us+national+news+site:apnews.com","JetZero plans to build $4.7B plant in North Carolina, aims to create 14,500 jobs","https://apnews.com/article/north-carolina-airplane-plant-jetzero-fdb49ed6c9d38981765ef1f421e3357a","Thu, 12 Jun 2025 18:58:00 GMT","




